Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.92,0:00:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復得不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.16,0:00:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是不能勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.37,0:00:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 感覺輕鬆多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天這樣會用光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.01,0:00:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些螃蟹和牡蠣的屍體還不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是食人族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.68,0:00:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的故鄉到底是個怎樣的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.60,0:00:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說了 妖精之鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是浮在遙遠的西海上的烏托邦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.98,0:00:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡鳥語花香 以下略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖 妖精地獄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.20,0:00:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是地獄 是妖精之鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多你這種貨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾聽師傅大人說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.37,0:00:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位於西海裡傳說的島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.67,0:00:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫斯基利格島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.79,0:00:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和靈樹森林一樣屬於狹間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.46,0:01:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航海圖上沒有記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.47,0:01:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人也無法到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.47,0:01:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個島上有很多魔術師和精靈一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.39,0:01:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 希凱兒妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.81,0:01:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個不情之請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.73,0:01:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能教我魔術嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這又是哪一齣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.49,0:01:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露姐姐當魔女嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.79,0:01:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從獸鬼的事以後 我一直在考慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.79,0:01:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 你一個大人要當這個小毛孩的徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候說實話我很觸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.18,0:01:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所弓發的奇蹟 魔法的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.43,0:01:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也會有必須保護別人的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.77,0:01:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我勇氣的是喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你給我的一把魔法短劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.94,0:02:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那只是把銀刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.32,0:02:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 就是如假包換的魔法短劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科羅拉說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.41,0:02:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受巨大的謎團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在世界之中探求萬事萬物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.25,0:02:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是魔道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有能照亮未知的黑暗的光明的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就請授予我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.84,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別盯著看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.64,0:02:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來不是從出生就開始學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能很好的理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.19,0:02:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且更關鍵的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.86,0:02:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的年齡越大就越會被眼前的名為現世的世界觀束縛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.99,0:02:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將這種固有觀念打破是很難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.07,0:02:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是遇到不少可怕事情的法露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不用擔心這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己尚在修行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也會力所能及地教你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.71,0:03:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 法露小姐 要當魔女?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.47,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼趕快教我咒文吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要從基礎開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 希凱兒 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.82,0:04:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上的大海有點怕怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在散步嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.91,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實在這月色下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太容易入睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.79,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.76,0:05:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次看到大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海連通著幽界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美麗又溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕又恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣觸動扣人心弦的風景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.44,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的地方必定連接著幽界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候雖然也想像過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣站在海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才第一次明白師傅所言的含義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經踏上了無法回頭的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那樣用小聰明去自己處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然擔心他人也許能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時令你忘記自己的憂愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小就老這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會變成世故的大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我們魔術師來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.82,0:06:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和親人的生離死別和你們現世的人的含義不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.21,0:06:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對身處現世和幽界的魔術士來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡不是完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是羽化為新的偉大生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.22,0:06:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對 絶對不會悲痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.57,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算好受些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛和鼻子因為海風有點痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.99,0:07:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也一樣 全身痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然在硬撐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.76,0:07:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 希凱兒也長大了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒想到第一次的對象是這種大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡比自己大的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.35,0:07:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但確實比那兩個強一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.31,0:07:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會對狂野大叔第一次敞開少女的青澀情懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.36,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 心裡癢癢的 無法自拔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.07,0:07:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話我原樣奉還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近欠了你不少人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.67,0:07:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是現在才開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且先道個謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你這次有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛失去幾種顔色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌頭失去味覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.60,0:08:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指尖顫抖疲憊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是預兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.78,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你身穿那副甲冑作為狂戰士戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明 聲音 溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.91,0:08:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會失去許多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不討人喜歡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是那樣無所不知的囗氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再那麼狼狽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.34,0:08:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我會讓你看到我好好用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.64,0:08:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我不會讓那種事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前讓你多費心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.52,0:08:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我失禮 你和師博大人是什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.99,0:09:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幅甲冑原本是你穿的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是好友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.75,0:09:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點像你們現在這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿在這甲冑上的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像絶不會熄滅的火焰一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.09,0:09:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算曾經控制住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火種也會繼續存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一有機會就會輕易地化為業火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有護符保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.02,0:09:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你還想保有人的身份的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的親切關懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.65,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼親切能不能告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.83,0:09:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙 那些使徒何要襲擊婆婆的洋館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹現在是現世之外的超然存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.05,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以想像現世有人能威脅他的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.64,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就好比在故事中登場的人物要挑戰作者一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能挑戰鷹 要想威脅到他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.65,0:10:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有和他一樣是故事外的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為個他就把師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.28,0:10:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個魔法師比起千軍萬馬更讓他忌憚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們繼續旅程的話 很快就會再次和使徒碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.63,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.01,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後到那時 率領他們的恐怕就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.14,0:10:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.86,0:11:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保護還是要挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就繼續追問你的靈魂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以人類之軀矗立於狹間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一個希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要去的妖精之鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名為花吹雪王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頗有力量而在傳說中傳頌的妖精王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.40,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是魔導書中被記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.32,0:11:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在很多的詩歌和故事中都有他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋 這種事一個字也沒說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.70,0:11:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我疏忽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.12,0:11:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統冶巴克故鄉的是那樣的大妖精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助他的力量就能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你的愛人烙印女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.55,0:12:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復本心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不說假話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.68,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復原 她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.57,0:12:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.32,0:12:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的願望不一定完全是那個女孩期望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.50,0:12:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.63,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 說起花吹雪王就是在廣為傳頌的偉大的妖精王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厲害的嗎你們的王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼瞞著我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.78,0:13:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的願望不一定就完全是她的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著大霧 有什麼來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時一樣的死靈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣 好久不練身體都鈍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.53,0:13:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這股氣 比起死靈更像入侵洋館的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.85,0:14:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓動物被某種靈附身做出來的魔法生命體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是統稱的使魔的一種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依巴蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜是滿月 是最能發揮魔法威力的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.82,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不在寺院 也能施展四方之王陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在法術發動之氣 請拖延一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露小姐 保護好喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生 你的身體還不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動活動遲鈍的身體正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.52,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這麼龐大也出不去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.56,0:15:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用這東西餵飽它們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嚐嚐本大爺自創劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然看穿了我的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是照敵人嘴裡滾過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就是這個節奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真強 完全復原了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.32,0:15:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.94,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑在嗅血的氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在尋找爆發的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要意識混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將甲冑的力量最小限度發揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.37,0:16:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是抑制疼痛讓身體活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.17,0:16:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執掌韆繩的 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 來了來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趕緊幹點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.64,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巪魯可圖 阿忒 蓋不魯 蓋德魯 魯 阿蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.94,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是一如既往的華麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.94,0:16:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚看起來很像極光啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.44,0:16:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.03,0:16:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時這間屋子周圍安全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.78,0:16:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對於有肉體的他們防壁的力量是有限的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.17,0:16:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱大群怪物的施術者一定就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是打倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託趕快 大魔法師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.01,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 暫停 暫停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.93,0:17:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追樅氣流的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.44,0:17:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.57,0:17:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在海岸岩石背面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要逃趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.09,0:17:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 庫夏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 趕緊離開那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比巨鬼還大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.74,0:18:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大的話 我的防壁防不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準眼睛的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽路畢克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱它的術士在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼怪力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要是還要戰鬥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.42,0:19:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然厲害 面對那種大傢伙一點也不舊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.59,0:19:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你做成沙西米啊 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.50,0:20:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那樣瘍囗就又...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來引導他回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海吼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我捲入深深的水底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發出巨大轟鳴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.95,0:21:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.12,0:21:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據傳說 被稱為狂戰士的人不止敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.54,0:21:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己人都會感到恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.71,0:21:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 那麼猛烈的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此 附近的一切都會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不問敵我 一同斬斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.39,0:22:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵 懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牙 眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.27,0:22:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.27,0:22:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺 滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.65,0:22:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪 凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.44,0:22:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.25,0:22:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這要 來真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.01,0:22:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 還不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.01,0:22:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.44,0:22:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.65,0:22:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凝視吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.40,0:22:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傾聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.45,0:22:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.16,0:23:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.33,0:23:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.16,0:23:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.88,0:23:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.80,0:23:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回神了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.43,0:23:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.10,0:23:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.31,0:23:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是 和他說的一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.28,0:23:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.78,0:23:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己默默承受一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.45,0:23:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會變成彆扭的大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.12,0:23:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.04,0:23:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.89,0:00:10.28,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,看著很好吃 這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.13,0:00:13.50,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,比耶卑斯風海味火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.29,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.80,0:24:05.59,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}帶我過來辛苦了 我也來幫忙
